reviews.review_data: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2020
reviews.name: AstorDragon
reviews.title: Good so far
reviews.review: So far so good. I've seen a great improvement in the speed and ability to multitask over my 4 year old comparable computer. I'd like it to be a bit heavier to make it feel less fragile when I carry it around, but I know lightweight is more important to most people.
